I can see why this has 4.9 stars! It deserves 100000000000000000000000000000000000 stars <3 This is the best Toca Kitchen app by far! ;D You can roll up the sushi practically any way, make fun food shapes, choose your outside (seaweed, lettuce, and a couple of Unknown substances- maybe meat and dough?), and discover fun reactions from each customer! :3 Be aware, you can't choose your customer- they come in on their own. But, you can go to the serving area and kick them out- that's the only way to make them go, but when you make them go at the end of a meal, I see it as leaving, not _making_ them leave. To change your wrapper, simply go to the wrapping place and tap on it. It goes in the order: seaweed, lettuce, dough?, and meat?. Anyway, despite the price, this is like, the best sushi app EVER! You guys should totally get this. Yes, I'm aware this review is really long, I just have so many positive things to say about this app... Lol. :3 Bye now, tho.
